(How it works \(repo-evidence architecture\)) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 52 528 Tm
( - UI layer: index.html defines board/HUD/buttons; styles.css defines layout/theme/responsive controls.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 52 516 Tm
( - Runtime/controller: src/game.js binds DOM events, maps inputs, runs setInterval\(140ms\), and renders.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 52 504 Tm
( - Logic module: src/snake.js exports pure state functions for init, movement, collisions, and food.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 52 492 Tm
( - Data flow: input -> setDirection/togglePause -> step\(state\) per tick -> state -> DOM + HUD update.) Tj
ET
BT
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 52 480 Tm
( - Tests: tests/snake.test.mjs validates movement, growth, collisions, reverse rule, and food placement.) Tj
